      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>basa fillets</strong> in the <strong>flour</strong>, tap off the excess, then add them into the <strong>beaten egg</strong></p><p>Finally press them into the <strong>panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over – this is your <strong>breaded fish</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
