    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Cut the<strong> lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into quarters</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (don't like raw garlic? Go easy!), <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>clotted cream</strong> and the juice of 1<strong> </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>lemon quarter<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in a small bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>garlic butter</strong></p>",
