      "instruction": "<p>Trims the <strong>green beans</strong></p><p>Once the potatoes are almost fork-tender, add the<strong> green beans</strong> to the pot and cook for a further 3-4 min or until tender with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain and return them to the pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, the <strong>juice</strong> of <strong>1 </strong><span class=\"text-danger\">[2]</span> <strong>lemon quarter<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p>",
